---
// src/pages/index.astro
import '../styles/landing.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MariaCRM | Gerencie Grupos de WhatsApp e Acelere suas Vendas</title>
    <!-- Google Material Symbols -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" rel="stylesheet" />
    <meta name="description" content="O CRM que se conecta diretamente ao WhatsApp. Gerencie grupos, importe leads automaticamente e feche mais negócios. Planos a partir de R$100/mês.">
    <style>
        /* ── Pricing ── */
        .pricing-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            background: var(--bg-app);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        .plan-card {
            background: var(--bg-white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .plan-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
        .plan-card.popular {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--primary), 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(139, 46, 252, 0.2);
        }
        .popular-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -14px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 0.35rem 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.3rem;
        }
        .popular-badge .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;
        }
        .plan-name {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .plan-description {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .plan-price {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 0.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .plan-price .currency {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .plan-price .amount {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .plan-price .period {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .plan-billing {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .plan-divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }
        .plan-features {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .plan-features li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-body);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .plan-features li .check-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: var(--primary-light);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }
        .plan-features li .check-icon svg {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        .plan-cta {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .plan-cta.primary {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(139, 46, 252, 0.35);
        }
        .plan-cta.primary:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(139, 46, 252, 0.3);
        }
        .plan-cta.outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }
        .plan-cta.outline:hover {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .plan-cta.dark {
            background: var(--text-dark);
            color: white;
        }
        .plan-cta.dark:hover {
            background: #374151;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .enterprise-value {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* ── WhatsApp Integration Hero Card ── */
        .wpp-highlight {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #16a34a;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .wpp-highlight svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

        /* ── Stats bar ── */
        .stats-bar {
            background: var(--text-dark);
            padding: 1.75rem 0;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
            display: block;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .stat-divider {
            width: 1px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        /* ── WhatsApp Float Button ── */
        .wpp-float {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            background: #25D366;
            color: white;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            z-index: 100;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .wpp-float:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.5);
        }
        .wpp-float svg { width: 30px; height: 30px; }

        /* ── How it works ── */
        .how-section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .step-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .step-number {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
        }
        .step-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }
        .step-card p {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* ── Nav action button ── */
        .btn-wpp-nav {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: #25D366;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-wpp-nav:hover {
            background: #1fa855;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .btn-wpp-nav svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats-grid { gap: 2rem; }
            .stat-divider { display: none; }
            .plan-card.popular { margin-top: 1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- WhatsApp Float -->
    <a href="https://wa.me/557734212083" target="_blank" class="wpp-float" id="wpp-float-btn" title="Fale no WhatsApp">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
        </svg>
    </a>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container header-content">
            <a href="/" class="brand">
                <div class="brand-icon">M</div>
                MariaCRM
            </a>
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <a href="#como-funciona" class="nav-link">Como funciona</a>
                <a href="#recursos" class="nav-link">Recursos</a>
                <a href="#planos" class="nav-link">Planos</a>
            </nav>
            <div class="actions">
                <a href="https://wa.me/557734212083" target="_blank" class="btn-wpp-nav">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Falar com consultor
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero container">
            <div class="wpp-highlight">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
                </svg>
                Integração nativa com WhatsApp — sem intermediários
            </div>

            <h1>Transforme Grupos de WhatsApp<br/><span>em Clientes no seu CRM</span></h1>
            <p>
                Importe contatos com 1 clique, organize seu funil e feche mais vendas em um único lugar.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-pills">
                <span class="pill-tag"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">groups</span> Grupos de WhatsApp</span>
                <span class="pill-tag"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">bolt</span> Importação de Leads</span>
                <span class="pill-tag"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">filter_alt</span> Múltiplos Funis</span>
                <span class="pill-tag"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">group</span> Usuários Ilimitados</span>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="#planos" class="btn-primary" id="hero-cta-planos">
                    Ver Planos e Preços
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/557734212083" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary" id="hero-cta-wpp">
                    Falar com consultor
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Stats Bar -->
        <div class="stats-bar">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">Ilimitado</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Usuários no plano</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Integração WhatsApp</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">1-clique</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Importação de contatos</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">R$100</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">A partir de / mês</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Como Funciona -->
        <section id="como-funciona" class="how-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Da prospecção ao fechamento, tudo integrado</h2>
                    <p>Conecte seu WhatsApp e comece a capturar leads dos seus grupos de forma automática e organizada.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="steps-grid">
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h3>Conecte seu WhatsApp</h3>
                        <p>Escaneie o QR Code e vincule sua conta. A integração é direta, sem apps de terceiros.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h3>Sincronize seus grupos</h3>
                        <p>Todos os grupos em que você está aparecem no painel com nome, participantes e link de convite.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h3>Importe os contatos</h3>
                        <p>Com um clique, os participantes viram leads na sua base — com número, nome e origem registrados.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-card">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <h3>Gerencie no funil</h3>
                        <p>Mova negociações entre etapas, atribua vendedores e feche contratos com total visibilidade.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Recursos: WhatsApp + Funis -->
        <section id="recursos" class="feature-block">
            <div class="container feature-content">
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <span class="subtitle-badge"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat_bubble</span> WhatsApp Nativo</span>
                    <h2>Grupos de WhatsApp viram sua maior fonte de leads</h2>
                    <p>O MariaCRM se conecta diretamente ao WhatsApp — sem aplicativos intermediários. Você sincroniza grupos, extrai participantes e já inicia as negociações, tudo dentro do CRM.</p>

                    <div class="accordion-wrapper" style="margin: 0; max-width: 100%;">
                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <details open>
                                <summary>
                                    <div class="acc-title">
                                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                                        Importação de participantes em 1 clique
                                    </div>
                                    <svg class="chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="accordion-content">
                                    Todos os participantes do grupo são importados automaticamente como contatos no CRM, com número de telefone e origem registrados. Nada de copiar e colar manualmente.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <details>
                                <summary>
                                    <div class="acc-title">
                                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
                                        Link de convite e gestão de grupos
                                    </div>
                                    <svg class="chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="accordion-content">
                                    Gere e atualize links de convite dos grupos diretamente pelo painel. Visualize todos os grupos sincronizados com total participantes e histórico de leads importados.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>

                        <div class="accordion-item">
                            <details>
                                <summary>
                                    <div class="acc-title">
                                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
                                        Rastreio de leads por campanha e origem
                                    </div>
                                    <svg class="chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                                </summary>
                                <div class="accordion-content">
                                    Saiba de qual grupo veio cada lead, qual campanha trouxe mais fechamentos e quanto cada canal contribuiu para sua receita.
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-visual">
                    <div class="mockup-window" style="width:85%;">
                        <div class="mockup-header">
                            <div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div><div class="mockup-dot"></div>
                            <span style="margin-left: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #9ca3af; font-family: monospace;">Grupos WhatsApp</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mockup-body" style="gap: 0.75rem;">
                            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; background:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:8px; padding:0.6rem 0.85rem;">
